House Price Prediction – 
Readme file - UI/UX Implementation

This project predicts house prices using a trained Machine Learning model.
The model takes inputs like square footage, number of bathrooms, balconies, and distance to metro, and displays the predicted price through a Streamlit web interface.
 Features
Predict house prices using trained ML model
Interactive web interface using Streamlit
User-friendly number input fields
Displays predicted price in Lakhs and Rupees
Shows affordability status (Affordable / Expensive)

Technologies Used
Python
Streamlit
NumPy
Pickle
Scikit-learn (for model training)
VS Code (for development)

